## UI, Design System, and Styling

- Component library: `@gluestack-ui/themed@^1.1.73` (v1 final â€” no further releases), `@gluestack-ui/config@^1.1.20` (v1 final). These packages provide structural primitives (a11y, focus management, compound components); component-level themes are **stripped** in `src/lib/gluestack/gluestack-ui.config.ts` so NativeWind remains the sole styling layer.
- Styling bridge: `nativewind@^4.2.4` with `tailwindcss@^3.4.19` (dev, v3-LTS line). **Do NOT upgrade to Tailwind v4** â€” NativeWind v4 is only compatible with Tailwind v3. NativeWind v5 (preview) would support Tailwind v4 but is not stable.
